# Trimmed MySQL func_concat.test for RooDB compatibility testing.
# Original: /usr/lib/mysql-test/t/func_concat.test (153 lines)
#

# [RooDB-skip] --source include/turn_off_only_full_group_by.inc
# [RooDB-skip] GROUP BY with non-aggregated columns (lines 11-31)
# [RooDB-skip] UNION queries (lines 43-74)
# [RooDB-skip] Stored procedures (lines 125-153)
# [RooDB-skip] ANALYZE TABLE (line 109)
# [RooDB-skip] EXPLAIN (lines 115-116)
